headline: Trust is Under Attack: AI and Automation Fuel a New Wave of Targeted Cybercrime
summary: Gen (NASDAQ: GEN), a global leader powering Digital Freedom with a family of trusted brands including Norton, Avast, LifeLock, MoneyLion and more, today released its Q3 2025 Gen Threat Report, looking at trends from July through September.
